data.description: This charming bungalow in Weston, OR., nestled by Pine Creek, has been completely renovated with meticulous attention to detail. From its inviting warm interior & exterior paint colors to the gray/brown wood laminate flooring, every corner exudes a delightful ambiance.Explore the country kitchen with soft close drawers, & farm house sink to the inviting primary bedroom featuring a stunning tiled bathroom & spacious walk-in closet. It offers year-round comfort with three ductless mini-split heat pumps, newer double-pane vinyl windows, & a spacious deck for BBQs. The property features a concrete parking slab with 50-amp service for an RV, surrounded by a new fence, and includes three storage buildings, one perfect for DIY/hobby enthusiasts.
